name: @babel/plugin-proposal-class-properties
notes: Babel plugin for transforming class properties syntax during build/compilation. Part of Babel's code transformation ecosystem - designed for build pipelines (webpack, esbuild, vite) to transpile modern JavaScript features into older syntax. Not a runtime library. Like @babel/cli, @babel/core, and other Babel plugins, this is for development/build workflows, not serverless execution.
errorMessage: Expected opts.sync to be a function.
